Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有『结果』这个答案在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未有过例外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 鲁路修的力量起不了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使拥有着对任何对手都能下达绝对服从命令的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.19,0:00:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法从那个必然下逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了替母亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修为了创造妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界而行动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是世界 人们却总是把和他的预想不同的结果摆在他眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并追求结果的『继续』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这个『继续』与世界结合起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些人必须背负的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所应得到的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在何处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 14
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}GEASS 对 GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥呼叫401
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续反击敌人并向9点方向移动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后将归入西宁格卿的指挥下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别深追了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在保护总督是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回话啊 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没事但现在无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来发布撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟疑的话会被全灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见啊 竟然动摇到无法发布指令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是科奈莉娅的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 枪不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我晕过去的那段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被什么人拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的样子被人看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少被两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪的和被射击的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是情书之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是鲁路修吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见由菲米娅殿下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢…想说一下感谢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭店劫持事件时她挺身保护了妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出自己是由菲米娅 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能入赘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为有这种不单纯的思想的话是见不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉还真是严格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 会长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算鲁路修不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也别把这种越线的行为冲着我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也想见一见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见由菲米娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 对方是高不可攀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是阿修佛德学园学生会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那儿有什么不平常的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉好像也没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近上课也请假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是要做的更像学生一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你这个优等生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能转告一下娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会晚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是“今天会”而是“今天也”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是见不到面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要在同一所学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在玩什么啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 朱雀好像不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来被军队看到的可能消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为军队和黑色骑士团以外还有人会去那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有日本解放战线的幸存者这一可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只偷了枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让扇注意黑市的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然采取了但太花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是好像在战场上看到了莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 和你接吻的那个女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想确认一下 你这个好色的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话她就是我们现在的主要目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是这次的作战还是成田连山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明显是针对公主的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准首领是战争的正统方案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克洛维斯殿下的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说ZERO对于布里塔尼亚的体制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如说他可能是以对布里塔尼亚皇族的仇恨来行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护人质而挺身而出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心啊 由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想再见到饭店劫持那样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要招入骑士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为警卫的由菲米娅大人的专任骑士的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能以那人为中心构筑亲卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲米娅大人是副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经有那样的权利了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初认为他只是比较温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:07:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不认为他对人命的态度太过激了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动数据并没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想顺便试一下那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那还在调整中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你完全不顾我说的不要把朱雀当成零件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好面对他的话会无法看清一切 无法好好传达的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你才是没有把他和某人重叠起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是能注意到奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说我也是你的上司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等房间的杀菌消毒结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非得检查别人的内衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人情可是很贵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你干的还真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人应该不会介意让喜欢的男人来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又对奇怪的地方过于执着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没找到枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日记也只写到14天以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她父亲死去的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为嫌疑犯来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用这种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错的慰灵碑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉·菲耐特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次连那白壳的家伙也一起打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:08:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉成一下子就被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放战线的船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么爆炸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自爆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有过联络吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来救援
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了那个ZERO才行动的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是见到脸的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你在怀疑ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说时机太巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是ZERO所做的话你想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那种口气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 迪哈鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你好像害怕的逃跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是胆小的布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用这种口气对我们干部说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要掌握战场的情况而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇也承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO也说没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫莎莉的那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么要去成田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是因为有可能被知道了身份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决掉她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正不想失去的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该远离她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生存的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修真是过分的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你对鲁鲁的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被骗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他其实是ZERO的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用下令造成你父亲死去的那张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺去了你的吻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅呢 这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是让人吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生自己是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把这家伙交给科奈莉娅总督
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能成为贵族了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是骑士侯而是真正的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的处刑会比较适合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督也会对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是你的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和ZERO同罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且以父亲的死作为交换代价
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我是 我是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了期待从他那里得到温柔故意表现得很可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同情的视线很舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要装成悲剧的女主角到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想过那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了救男人而杀人的你不是什么女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是丑恶的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道鲁路修喜欢别的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想呆在他的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该受到报应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要一生背负这种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个人来背负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法弥补罪孽就无法解脱内心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和鲁路修真是太可怜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来认为会是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有分头去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吧 莎莉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到现在还说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会在的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被知道了的话怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决掉她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙和莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新再从头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对莎莉做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅自己的女人被夺走的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么来决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对这个比较在行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我画的话能用巴土安画风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[巴土安画风(Batuan style):巴厘岛的一种绘画流派风格]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我等到你画完吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托军队或警察的话会比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想招惹没有必要的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么到高处去找怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修这家伙在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下棋估计只是一个幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的目的是把我带到无人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是第一次玩这个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用手机只是演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是因为不知道我的长相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说没有时间得到我的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是周详准备过的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是把注意力集中在胜负上比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会输的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么第一次玩 你这个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 正是因为是你所以才胜不了毛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这样可以算是我的胜利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然会被完全看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听C.C.说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在一瞬间想到了14种答案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且其中之一是完全正确
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的Geass如果没有直接看到对方的眼睛就没法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些规则我也全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能读出我的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的就是这样的Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对莎莉开枪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你对莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始惩罚游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的你不像平常的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有这种感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的…鲁鲁的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Geass吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该还没对她用过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果你这么做的话就会马上开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看透的只是表象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有和我一样使用Geass的条件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:16:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动时机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要杀掉我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你得意的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕噜咕噜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于当小偷的猫来说这种死法才适合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补偿自己的罪孽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会陪你一起死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对另一个目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护你的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 那个血迹是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束吧 鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于罪孽就是要用惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙对莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够读懂思考的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵人 对其进行诱导就很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 正是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被骗了 莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗了她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了人是罪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要再让罪孽增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 真会说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的杀了人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是被那家伙诱导了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是自己发觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直隐瞒下去是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在犹豫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可是杀了你的父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙只是杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考真是乱的一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就随你们两个人的便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想弄得戏剧性一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把两个人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来了吗 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 毛 你不是能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种打扮也很美啊 C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C. 我会来见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会来见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然会出现在人群之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开枪射了人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还开枪射了鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我射了鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的罪全部由我来承担
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要你对我温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸明明死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的事全部忘记就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来让你全部忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲的事很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够重生一次的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也失去了家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 大概是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事是失去之后才第一次明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己曾那么的被她的笑容所拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样的拌嘴也能笑着去回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然已经忘了到刚才为止自己为什么要到这儿来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这也是什么契机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不可能忘掉想忘掉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有很多悲伤的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是黎明总是会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别再一直消沉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我是比较天真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许除掉莎莉更好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:24:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass 如果说这个力量会使人孤独的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.59,0:24:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要有更能忍受的精神才行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.56,0:24:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后对毛 把这个仇…
